HEADWORD: Unflesh
<hw>Un*flesh"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>flesh</ets>.]</ety> <def>To deprive of flesh; to
reduce a skeleton.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Unfleshed</xex> humanity.⟦rdquo⟧
